What you need to know:  Unhappy Paris Saint-Germain fans targeted the Argentine as well as Neymar during the 3-0 win over Bordeaux that followed the club's spectacular Champions League elimination at the hands of Real Madrid.Adored in Barcelona, from where he made a tearful exit last August, the seven-time Ballon d'Or winner suddenly found himself in a position he had never previously experienced during his remarkable club career.